  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"mc-hero-strip\">\n<div class=\"container mc-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"mc-hero-copy\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb mc-breadcrumb\">\n<a href=\"/resources\">资源中心</a>\n<span>/</span>\n<b>模型社区</b>\n</div>\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">MODEL COMMUNITY</span>\n<h1>制造人的 3D 模型开源社区</h1>\n<p>\n          浏览、收藏、评论和下载其他用户分享的工业零部件模型。\n          支持 CNC、3D 打印、钣金、注塑、铸造等制造场景。\n        </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-hero-actions\">\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">\n          上传模型\n        </a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n          发布规范\n        </a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mc-community-section\">\n<div class=\"container mc-community-layout\">\n<aside class=\"mc-left-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>模型频道</h3>\n<nav aria-label=\"模型频道筛选\" class=\"mc-channel-nav\">\n<button aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"model-category-button active\" data-model-filter=\"all\" type=\"button\">\n<span>推荐</span>\n<b>全部模型</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"cnc\" type=\"button\">\n<span>CNC</span>\n<b>数控加工</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"3dprint\" type=\"button\">\n<span>PRINT</span>\n<b>3D 打印</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"sheet\" type=\"button\">\n<span>SHEET</span>\n<b>钣金加工</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"injection\" type=\"button\">\n<span>MOLD</span>\n<b>注塑模具</b>\n</button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"model-category-button\" data-model-filter=\"casting\" type=\"button\">\n<span>CAST</span>\n<b>铸造结构</b>\n</button>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>常用格式</h3>\n<div class=\"mc-format-cloud\">\n<span>STEP</span>\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>STL</span>\n<span>OBJ</span>\n<span>DXF</span>\n<span>SLDPRT</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card mc-upload-mini\">\n<h3>贡献模型</h3>\n<p>\n            上传可公开模型，补充材料、工艺、格式和设计说明。\n          </p>\n<a href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">\n            立即发布 →\n          </a>\n</div>\n</aside>\n<section class=\"mc-feed\">\n<div class=\"mc-feed-top\">\n<form class=\"mc-search-bar\" role=\"search\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></circle>\n<path d=\"M20 20l-4.3-4.3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path>\n</svg>\n<input aria-label=\"搜索模型\" id=\"model-search-input\" placeholder=\"搜索模型、材料、工艺、格式，例如：铝合金 支架 STEP\" type=\"search\"/>\n</form>\n<div class=\"mc-sort-box\">\n<select aria-label=\"模型排序\" id=\"model-sort-select\">\n<option value=\"hot\">综合热度</option>\n<option value=\"downloads\">下载最多</option>\n<option value=\"likes\">点赞最多</option>\n<option value=\"latest\">最新发布</option>\n</select>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-feed-tabs\">\n<button class=\"is-active\" type=\"button\">推荐</button>\n<button type=\"button\">最新</button>\n<button type=\"button\">关注</button>\n<button type=\"button\">问答</button>\n<span id=\"model-result-count\">共 8 个模型</span>\n<button class=\"mc-clear-button\" id=\"model-clear-filter\" type=\"button\">\n            清空筛选\n          </button>\n</div>\n<article class=\"mc-composer-card\">\n<div class=\"mc-composer-avatar\">M</div>\n<div class=\"mc-composer-body\">\n<strong>分享一个模型，或者发起制造讨论</strong>\n<p>\n              可以发布模型文件、结构设计问题、加工工艺建议、DFM 疑问或材料选型经验。\n            </p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">\n                上传模型\n              </a>\n<a href=\"/resources/design-guidelines\">\n                查看发布规范\n              </a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"cnc\" data-comments=\"42\" data-downloads=\"1280\" data-format=\"STEP\" data-hot=\"96\" data-keywords=\"CNC 数控加工 不锈钢 轴类 STEP 键槽 螺纹\" data-latest=\"8\" data-likes=\"236\" data-material=\"不锈钢\" data-model-id=\"precision-shaft\" data-title=\"精密轴类零件 STEP 模型\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">L</div>\n<div>\n<strong>结构设计师 Leo</strong>\n<span>2 小时前 · 发布到 CNC 加工频道</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>\n              精密轴类零件 STEP 模型，适合车削报价和图纸标注参考\n            </h2>\n<p>\n              模型包含多台阶轴、键槽、螺纹、倒角和退刀槽结构。\n              适合用于 CNC 车削工艺评估、轴类零件公差标注参考，也可以作为报价前模型检查样例。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>CNC 加工</span>\n<span>不锈钢</span>\n<span>STEP</span>\n<span>轴类零件</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>CNC 工艺工程师 Chen：</strong>\n                键槽和退刀槽处理比较完整，建议补一版带关键轴径公差的工程图。\n              </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"236\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>236</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>收藏</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"precision-shaft\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>42 评论</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"precision-shaft\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"精密轴类零件 STEP 模型\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>分享</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"precision-shaft\" type=\"button\">\n                查看详情\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"模型预览（当前为图片占位，后续接入 3D 渲染）\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"精密轴类零件模型\" src=\"/precision/service-cnc.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>STEP</span>\n<span>CNC</span>\n</div></div>\n\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>precision-shaft.step</b>\n<span>STEP · 2.8 MB · 适合 CNC 车削</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/precision-shaft.step\">\n                下载模型\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"3dprint\" data-comments=\"35\" data-downloads=\"856\" data-format=\"STL\" data-hot=\"92\" data-keywords=\"3D打印 金属打印 钛合金 法兰 STL STEP 轻量化\" data-latest=\"7\" data-likes=\"198\" data-material=\"钛合金\" data-model-id=\"lightweight-flange\" data-title=\"轻量化法兰连接件\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">M</div>\n<div>\n<strong>3D 打印爱好者 Mina</strong>\n<span>今天 · 发布到 3D 打印频道</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>\n              轻量化法兰连接件 STL 模型，适合金属 3D 打印结构参考\n            </h2>\n<p>\n              这个模型保留了法兰安装孔位，并在中间区域加入减重结构和加强筋。\n              可以用来参考金属 3D 打印轻量化设计，也适合后续 CNC 二次加工讨论。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>3D 打印</span>\n<span>钛合金</span>\n<span>STL</span>\n<span>轻量化</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>材料工程师 Yuan：</strong>\n                如果实际使用钛合金，建议补充壁厚下限和后处理说明。\n              </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"198\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>198</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>收藏</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"lightweight-flange\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>35 评论</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"lightweight-flange\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"轻量化法兰连接件\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>分享</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"lightweight-flange\" type=\"button\">\n                查看详情\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"模型预览（当前为图片占位，后续接入 3D 渲染）\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"轻量化法兰连接件\" src=\"/precision/product-flange.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>STL</span>\n<span>3D PRINT</span>\n</div></div>\n\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>lightweight-flange.stl</b>\n<span>STL · 4.1 MB · 适合金属打印</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/lightweight-flange.stl\">\n                下载模型\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"sheet\" data-comments=\"76\" data-downloads=\"2110\" data-format=\"DXF\" data-hot=\"98\" data-keywords=\"钣金 支架 激光切割 折弯 DXF 铝合金 展开图\" data-latest=\"6\" data-likes=\"342\" data-material=\"铝合金\" data-model-id=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" data-title=\"钣金折弯支架\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">A</div>\n<div>\n<strong>自动化设备团队 AX Lab</strong>\n<span>昨天 · 发布到钣金加工频道</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>\n              钣金折弯支架 DXF 展开模型，已包含折弯线和安装孔位\n            </h2>\n<p>\n              适合自动化设备内部支架参考。模型中预留了安装孔、折弯线和加强边，\n              可用于激光切割、折弯工艺沟通，也适合做 DFM 检查示例。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>钣金</span>\n<span>铝合金</span>\n<span>DXF</span>\n<span>折弯</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>钣金工程师 Zhou：</strong>\n                建议发布时同步写清楚板厚和折弯半径，实际加工会更准确。\n              </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"342\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>342</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>收藏</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>76 评论</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"钣金折弯支架\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>分享</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"sheet-metal-bracket\" type=\"button\">\n                查看详情\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"模型预览（当前为图片占位，后续接入 3D 渲染）\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"钣金折弯支架\" src=\"/precision/insight-material.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>DXF</span>\n<span>SHEET</span>\n</div></div>\n\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>sheet-metal-bracket.dxf</b>\n<span>DXF · 1.3 MB · 含展开结构</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/sheet-metal-bracket.dxf\">\n                下载模型\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"cnc\" data-comments=\"31\" data-downloads=\"756\" data-format=\"IGES\" data-hot=\"81\" data-keywords=\"CNC 五轴 铝合金 IGES 腔体 曲面 异形零件\" data-latest=\"5\" data-likes=\"151\" data-material=\"铝合金\" data-model-id=\"complex-cavity\" data-title=\"复杂腔体零件\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">F</div>\n<div>\n<strong>五轴加工笔记</strong>\n<span>3 天前 · 发布到 CNC 加工频道</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>\n              复杂腔体 IGES 模型，适合五轴路径规划和装夹讨论\n            </h2>\n<p>\n              模型包含异形腔体、曲面过渡和多角度加工特征。\n              适合讨论五轴加工可达性、刀轴摆动、夹具避让和 CMM 检测方案。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>五轴加工</span>\n<span>铝合金</span>\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>复杂腔体</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>五轴编程 Kai：</strong>\n                这个模型建议增加基准面说明，否则装夹方案会有几种不同选择。\n              </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"151\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>151</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>收藏</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"complex-cavity\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>31 评论</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"complex-cavity\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"复杂腔体零件\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>分享</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"complex-cavity\" type=\"button\">\n                查看详情\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"模型预览（当前为图片占位，后续接入 3D 渲染）\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"复杂腔体零件\" src=\"/precision/factory-floor.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>5-AXIS</span>\n</div></div>\n\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>complex-cavity.iges</b>\n<span>IGES · 6.5 MB · 曲面腔体结构</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/complex-cavity.iges\">\n                下载模型\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<article class=\"mc-post-card model-library-card\" data-category=\"injection\" data-comments=\"21\" data-downloads=\"643\" data-format=\"IGES\" data-hot=\"75\" data-keywords=\"注塑 ABS 外壳 IGES 拔模 分型线 卡扣\" data-latest=\"4\" data-likes=\"126\" data-material=\"ABS\" data-model-id=\"injection-shell\" data-title=\"注塑设备外壳\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-main\">\n<div class=\"mc-post-author\">\n<div class=\"mc-avatar\">T</div>\n<div>\n<strong>模具工程师 Tang</strong>\n<span>4 天前 · 发布到注塑模具频道</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>\n              注塑外壳 IGES 模型，包含拔模斜度、卡扣位和分型线参考\n            </h2>\n<p>\n              适合做注塑结构设计参考。模型中包含外壳卡扣、薄壁结构、\n              拔模斜度和分型线区域，适合讨论注塑成型和模具设计风险。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"mc-post-tags\">\n<span>注塑</span>\n<span>ABS</span>\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>外壳结构</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-comments\">\n<p>\n<strong>结构设计师 Qian：</strong>\n                卡扣位置比较清楚，建议增加壁厚标注和筋位厚度说明。\n              </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-post-actions\">\n<button class=\"model-like-button\" data-count=\"126\" type=\"button\">\n<i>♡</i>\n<span>126</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-fav-button\" type=\"button\">\n<i>☆</i>\n<span>收藏</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-comment-button\" data-model-target=\"injection-shell\" type=\"button\">\n<i>💬</i>\n<span>21 评论</span>\n</button>\n<button class=\"model-share-button\" data-model-id=\"injection-shell\" data-model-share=\"\" data-share-title=\"注塑设备外壳\" type=\"button\">\n<i>↗</i><span>分享</span>\n</button><button class=\"model-detail-trigger\" data-model-target=\"injection-shell\" type=\"button\">\n                查看详情\n              </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<aside class=\"mc-post-preview model-card-media\">\n<div aria-label=\"模型预览（当前为图片占位，后续接入 3D 渲染）\" class=\"mc-preview-viewport\" data-model-viewport=\"\"><img alt=\"注塑设备外壳\" src=\"/precision/quality-process.jpg\"/><div class=\"mc-preview-badges\">\n<span>IGES</span>\n<span>MOLD</span>\n</div></div>\n\n<div class=\"mc-post-file\">\n<div>\n<b>injection-shell.iges</b>\n<span>IGES · 3.2 MB · 注塑外壳结构</span>\n</div>\n<a download=\"\" href=\"/models/injection-shell.iges\">\n                下载模型\n              </a>\n</div></aside>\n</article>\n<div class=\"model-empty-state\" hidden=\"\" id=\"model-empty-state\">\n<strong>暂未找到匹配模型</strong>\n<span>试试更换工艺分类，或搜索其他材料、格式、零件名称。</span>\n</div>\n</section>\n<aside class=\"mc-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"mc-side-card mc-profile-card\">\n<div class=\"mc-profile-avatar\">M</div>\n<h3>欢迎来到模型社区</h3>\n<p>\n            登录后可发布模型、收藏内容、参与评论，并管理自己的模型作品。\n          </p>\n<div>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/quote?mode=modelCommunity#quote-upload\">\n              上传\n            </a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>社区数据</h3>\n<div class=\"mc-stat-list\">\n<div>\n<strong>12,580+</strong>\n<span>开放模型</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>8,200+</strong>\n<span>活跃用户</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<strong>45,000+</strong>\n<span>月下载量</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mc-side-card\">\n<h3>热门话题</h3>\n<div class=\"mc-topic-list\">\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># STEP 和 IGES 哪个更适合 CNC 报价？</strong>\n<span>48 条讨论</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># 薄壁铝件模型上传前要标哪些关键尺寸？</strong>\n<span>32 条讨论</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># 3D 打印模型如何提前检查壁厚风险？</strong>\n<span>27 条讨论</span>\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\">\n<strong># 钣金展开图需要保留哪些信息？</strong>\n<span>19 条讨论</s